      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " مَا زَادَ عَلَى الْقَبْضَةِ فَفِي النَّارِ يَعْنِي اللِّحْيَةَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Muhammad Bin Abu Hamza, from the one who informed him, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Whatever increases upon the fist, so it is in the Fire’ – meaning the beard’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "10. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Muhammad ibn abu Hamzah from those who narrated to him has said the following: “Abu ‘ Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Whatever of beard exceeds the fist is in the fire.’” "
        ]
      }
